🧩 DIAGNOSTIC MODE: Step‑by‑Step Boot Sequence With Continue Buttons

This is a runtime troubleshooting overlay that appears before XR initialises.  
It lets you confirm each subsystem is alive.

This is the structure:

`
[1] Unity Scene Loaded
    [Continue]

[2] XR Loader Initialised
    [Continue]

[3] Passthrough Permission Granted
    [Continue]

[4] Passthrough Started
    [Continue]

[5] AR Camera Active
    [Continue]

[6] HUD Loaded
    [Continue]

[7] Mode Controller Started
    [Continue]

[8] Path Tracker Active
    [Continue]

[9] Coverage Map Active
    [Continue]

[10] Enter Game
`

If the app freezes before a step appears, you know exactly where the failure is.

