public enum SubsystemStatus { NotStarted, Initialising, Ok, Failed }

public class SubsystemHealth
{
    public SubsystemStatus xr;
    public SubsystemStatus passthrough;
    public SubsystemStatus arCamera;
    public SubsystemStatus hud;
    public SubsystemStatus modeController;
    public SubsystemStatus pathTracker;
    public SubsystemStatus coverageMap;
}
`

- TelemetryHUD MUST read from this model.  
- Each subsystem MUST update its own status.

Example:

- XR loader starts → xr = Initialising  
- XR loader success → xr = Ok  
- XR loader failure → xr = Failed + log error  

